SELECT DISTINCT SESSION_ID FROM PLAYBACK WHERE SESSION_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT SESSION_ID FROM PLAYBACK P LEFT JOIN ADS A USING(CUSTOMER_ID) WHERE TIMESTAMP BETWEEN START_TIME AND END_TIME)

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT P.SESSION_ID, SUM(IF(A.TIMESTAMP < P.START_TIME OR A.TIMESTAMP > P.END_TIME, 1, 0)) AS QUALIFIED_CNT, COUNT(AD_ID) AS TOTAL_CNT FROM PLAYBACK AS P INNER JOIN ADS AS A ON P.CUSTOMER_ID = A.CUSTOMER_ID GROUP BY P.SESSION_ID ) SELECT SESSION_ID FROM CTE WHERE QUALIFIED_CNT = TOTAL_CNT UNION ALL SELECT SESSION_ID FROM PLAYBACK WHERE CUSTOMER_ID NOT IN (SELECT CUSTOMER_ID FROM ADS)
